2. <strong>Summary of Text:</strong> A brief summary of the entire twenty-four books that comprise the story of <i>The Odyssey<i>, and a brief summary of the events of each twenty-four books.
3. <strong>Themes in Text:</strong> A list comprising most of the themes in <i>The Odyssey<i>, and thematic statements relating to the main quotes of the story.
4. <strong>Connections to Liturature:</strong> Detailing connections between <i>The Odyssey<i> and modern literary works, through direct retellings of <i>The Odyssey<i> to connections between narrative archetype. Summarizing the story and explaining its connection to <i>The Odyssey<i>.
